{"tid":1715054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大手足應承我","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:25:43.000Z","uid":332022,"like":70,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6e34bcbde55aacdaa9e6208bee34fec1984ada","tid":1715054,"uid":332022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"仲記得之前民間記者會，有記者問到如果出解放軍，示威者會點樣應付。 當時記者會答Be Water，返屋企瞓覺，風趣得黎又好有道理。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我明白今時唔同往日，我身邊好多人都係中大舊生，明白對中大個種bonding，外人係難以理解。<br />\n<br />\n但我懇求如果真係出到老解同實彈，千祈唔好死守，裝備太懸殊冇得打。 <br />\n<br />\n我明白我冇位何位置，亦都係no body，無資格去教前線ge你地點做。但希望大家要留有用之軀，他日係煲底相見。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n利申：大家千祈唔好做犯法事，支持和平理性表達意見"},{"pid":"e0caa7628ec90cefae06600c907c62b08e2cd350","tid":1715054,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙:bangbang::bangbang:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=538d2ecf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Sen Menendez 出聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatormenendez/status/1194349446349443072?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs%3D21&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=db926302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatormenendez%2Fstatus%2F1194349446349443072%3Fs